src:
Markizáčka v tango plavkách hore nohami. Také pozadie by ste nečakali
Redaktorka zverejnila poriadne sexy fotku.
03 Nov 2019, 11:00 by zv
Janka Slačková si pred pár dňami vychutnávala horúce letné počasie. Kým my sme zo skríň vyťahovali kabáty, markizácka redaktorka si vystačila s plavkami. Pre prácu modelky totiž vycestovala do Turecka, kde o jeseni ešte nechyrujú.
Krásna tmavovláska zverejnila z pracovnej cesty na Instagrame niekoľko záberov a medzi nimi ich bolo zopár aj v bikinách. Janka by vďaka tancu a športu mohla chodiť v plavkách pokojne celý rok.
Svoju vypracovanú postavu ukázala najmä na fotke, na ktorej má tango plavky a robí stojku vedľa palmy. Človek by ani nepovedal, aké má vypracované pozadie.



Zdroj:Instagram/jankasla
text:
Marquis in tango swimsuit upside down. You wouldn't expect such a background
The editor published a really sexy photo.
03 Nov 2019, 11:00 by Vol
Janka Slačková enjoyed the hot summer weather a few days ago. While we were pulling our coats out of the wardrobes, the Marquess editor managed to get along with the swimsuit. To work as a model traveled to Turkey, where the autumn still chyrují.
A beautiful brunette girl posted a few shots from a business trip to Instagram, including a few in bikinis. Thanks to her dance and sport, Janka could walk in a swimsuit all year round.
She showed her elaborated figure especially in the photo, where she has a tango swimsuit and does a handstand next to a palm tree. One would not even say what the background is.



Source: Instagram / jankasla
